ğŸ§  What is ArgoCD
Argo CD is a GitOps continuous delivery (CD) tool for Kubernetes.
Argo CD automatically deploys and syncs Kubernetes applications from Git to the cluster.

Key Real-Time Benefits of ArgoCD
1ï¸âƒ£ Self-Healing
If someone deletes a pod manually:
kubectl delete pod
â¡ ArgoCD recreates it automatically

2ï¸âƒ£ Easy Rollback
Bad deployment?
â¡ Roll back by reverting Git commit
â¡ ArgoCD redeploys automatically

3ï¸âƒ£ Audit & Security
Who changed what â†’ Git history
No cluster credentials in Jenkins
Read-only Git access

GitOps = Git is the only place where deployment changes are made
Argo CD is a GitOps-based continuous delivery tool that automatically deploys and synchronizes Kubernetes applications using Git as the source of truth.

GitOps is a deployment methodology where Git is used as the single source of truth for infrastructure and application configuration, and automated tools continuously 
synchronize the desired state with the actual state in Kubernetes.

